:: Forest Gwylan Eden Confrontation
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<if $phase is "Gwylan">>
	"Oh, good!" Gwylan says, clapping <<person2>><<his>> hands. "Let's go, <<pcpetname "Gwylan">>. I have a pot of tea waiting for you back at the shop."
	<br><br>

	Gwylan turns and heads into the bushes. You start to follow, then look back. Eden hasn't moved. <<person1>><<His>> sights are trained on you now. <<His>> finger tightens around the trigger.
	<br><br>

	At the last moment, <<he>> turns and fires. The bullet whizzes past you and embeds in a tree. Splinters shoot outward. <<stress 24>><<ggstress>>
	<br><br>

	You decide not to stick around. You rush off after Gwylan, and <<person2>><<he>> takes your arm when you catch up.
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Next|Forest Gwylan Eden Shop]]>><<pass 15>><<set $phase to "willing">><</link>>
	<br>
<<else>>
	<<if $worn.neck.name is "familiar collar" and $worn.neck.cursed is 1>>
		You open your mouth—
		<br><br>

		"Of course <<pshe>> wants to go with me," Gwylan interrupts, placing a gentle hand on the back of your neck. <<person2>><<His>> fingers brush your collar. "<span class="witch">Isn't that right? Go on, tell <<person1>><<him>>.</span>"
		<br><br>

		<<hypnosisText "The words in your throat are replaced.">> "That's right," you say, staring at Eden. "I want to go with Gwylan."
		<br><br>

		Eden's face doesn't change. "Okay. Now say it without being prompted."
		<br><br>

		Gwylan tuts. "You need to learn to take a hint, Eden. Come on, <<pcpetname "Gwylan">>. <span class="witch">We're going home.</span>" Gwylan takes your arm and heads into the bushes. <<hypnosisText "You follow.">>
		<br><br>

		<<link [[Next|Forest Gwylan Eden Shop]]>><<pass 15>><<set $phase to "kidnap">><</link>>
		<br>
	<<else>>
		"I want to go with Eden," you say. <<person1>>"<<Hes>> right. I've been away for too long. I don't want you to get hurt, either."
		<br><br>

		<<He>> holds out a hand, never looking away from Gwylan. You hurry to the relative safety of <<his>> side. <<He>> stays stiff up until <<his>> arm is around you. Then you feel <<him>> relax. <<His>> hand shakes on your waist.
		<br><br>

		<<person2>>Gwylan watches the two of you, <<his>> head tilting. "Of course," <<he>> says. "I have no intention of keeping you locked away." <<He>> flicks <<his>> glance to Eden. "But, Eden?"
		<br><br>

		"What?" Eden snaps.
		<br><br>

		"The forest has eyes." <<He>> looks between the two of you. For a moment, you think <<hes>> seeing something else, or someone else. "May you find your way home safely."
		<br><br>

		<<He>> turns and heads into the bushes. You watch <<him>> go. It isn't until <<hes>> gone that Eden lets out an explosive breath. <<person1>><<He>> turns to you, and <<his>> expression hardens. "Don't think you're off the hook."
		<br><br>

		<<endevent>><<npc Eden>><<person1>>

		<<link [[Next (0:30)|Eden Caged Caught]]>><<pass 30>><</link>>
		<br>
	<</if>>
<</if>>

