:: Forest Trio Confrontation Escape
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<npc Gwylan>><<person1>>
You end up in another small clearing. Gwylan pants, looking back into the trees. "Nature will take its course," <<he>> says between breaths. "Those two could never best one another. I doubt today will be any different."
<br><br>

<<if $phase is "front">>
	<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("partners")>>
		<<He>> pulls you into a kiss. <<gwylanKiss>>
		<br><br>

		<<He>> separates, and slaps you across the face. "Never do something so reckless ever again! Do you understand me?! What would I have done if you had gotten hurt?" Tears well up in <<his>> eyes. <<pain 2>><<gpain>>
	<<else>>
		<<He>> pulls you into a tight hug. "Never do something so reckless again!"
	<</if>>
	<br><br>

	<<He>> takes a few moments to calm down.
<<else>>
	<<He>> gives you a scolding look. "The next time I say run, that means run." It slowly turns into a smile. "I'm happy that you stuck by me, but that was dangerous."
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<if _gwylanStatus.includes("reunion")>>
	<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("partners")>>
		"Honestly, you're such trouble. First you disappear on me for weeks, and now this. Do you have any idea how worried I was? Where were you?" <<if _gwylanTF.revealed>><<His>> tail wags behind <<him>>.<</if>>
	<<else>>
		"Honestly, you're such trouble. I'm glad I found you. I haven't seen you in ages, I thought you were gone for good. What happened to you?"
	<</if>>
	<br><br>

	<<gwylanReunion>>
	<br><br>

	<<if _gwylanStatus.includes("badEndReady")>>
		<<if $phase is "front">>
			<<He>> continues hugging you.
		<<else>>
			<<He>> hugs you tightly.
		<</if>>
		<br><br>

		"Please, just let me hold you for a little while. I really though this would be the end. I thought I'd be alone again."
		<br><br>

		You feel the slightest pinprick in your arm. <<pain 2>><<gpain>>
		<br><br>

		<span class="purple">The forest starts to shift and distort.</span> Gwylan's face remains in perfect clarity at the center of your vision. <<He>> smiles sweetly, holding up a pink rose. Its stem drips red. <<hallucinogen 160>><<ggghallucinogens>>
		<br><br>

		The ground attacks you from below, but Gwylan guides you down slowly. "Shhh... just... a little longer."
		<br><br>

		<<hypnosisText "<<His>> sweet voice silences your thoughts, and you're no longer where you once were.">> <<His>> voice fades away with the rest of the forest.
		<br><br>

		<<silently>><<clotheson>><<endcombat>><</silently>>

		<<if _gwylanStatus.includes("aurigaScarConfront")>>
			<<link [[Everything fades to black...|Forest Shop Nowhere Passout]]>><<pass 1 hour>><<endevent>><</link>>
		<<else>>
			<<link [[Everything fades to black...|Forest Shop Taken Start]]>><<pass 1 hour>><<endevent>><</link>>
		<</if>>
	<<else>>
		<<He>> looks back into the treeline one last time. "Would you like to walk back to the shop with me? It would be safer together."
		<br><br>

		<<link [[Yes|Forest Gwylan Walk Shop]]>><<set $phase to 1>><<npcincr Gwylan dom 1>><</link>><<handholdingvirginitywarning>><<gyearning>>
		<br>
		<<link [[No|Forest Gwylan Walk Shop]]>><<set $phase to 2>><</link>>
		<br>
	<</if>>
<<else>>
	<<He>> looks back into the treeline one last time. "Would you like to walk back to the shop with me? It would be safer together."
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Yes|Forest Gwylan Walk Shop]]>><<set $phase to 1>><<npcincr Gwylan dom 1>><</link>><<handholdingvirginitywarning>><<gyearning>>
